text:
Remixing Super Mario Galaxy is really friggen hard.  The originals are pretty much perfect.

At least you managed to capture the tempo, beat, and notes.

Next steps for improvement would be to improve your sound quality and add your own interpretation to make it more original.

Add a synth line, incorporate bells, throw in a guitar solo. Do whatever feels right.

Keep working at it.
